author: Ruseberry
description:
Hello my loves,
Welcome to the most comforting, healing space on the internet. I'm here to welcome you to your new life of peace, abundance and beauty. My hope is for these videos to help you realize you can have whatever you want in this life the moment you learn to love yourself unconditionally.

A bit about me:
I'm of Ukrainian(dad) and Jamaican(mom) descent 🇺🇦🇯🇲. I grew up in Jamaica (Runaway Bay, St. Ann) but currently live in America (Florida). I have three brothers (one is my twin). During the days I work as a Senior UI/UX Web Developer (with the best team ever!) where I create and bring these designs to life in code.

Ruseberry 🌒🌕🌘 ♒️♉️♊️
